image.altText: Angus Brayshaw handballing during a 2023 AFL match.

image.altText: An aerial photo of an urban area with a river through the middle, and a green mountain range in the distance.

image.altText: A composite of a  tree-lined dirt track extending away into the bush, and a thin smiling woman with blonde hair.
